o-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104scm1665702798431.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/scm1665702798431.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/scm1665702798431.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"scm1665702798431\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Japanese Era \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to define a Japanese era of the emperors, for use with Kanji.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"scm1665702798431__p_d8537e1_d8538e1_d8539e1\">The traditional dating system in Japan as based on the reigns of the emperors. Uniface provides language setups for modern Japanese eras in <span class=\"ph filepath\">libmsg.usys.xml</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Modern Japanese Eras</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\"> Date</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">Japanese Era (Kanji)</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Japanese Era (Western)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\">1868-1912</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">明治</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Meiji</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\">1912-1926 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">大正</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Taishō</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\">1926-1989 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">昭和</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Shōwa</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\"> 1989-2019</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">平成</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Heisei</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__1\">2019 to present</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">令和</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"scm1665702798431__table_d935e1_d936e1_d937e1__entry__3\">Reiwa</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">You can use this dialog to define the available eras for the application.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"scm1665702798431__note_hxq_fmj_5cc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You must have the Kanji font available on your machine.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"scm1665702798431__section_cby_ylj_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221600e175\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"scm1665702798431__ul_t5d_zlj_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"scm1665702798431__li_d3953e1_d3954e1_d3955e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Begin Date</span> —date on which the\n          selected Japanese Era is to be applied. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"scm1665702798431__li_d3956e1_d3957e1_d3958e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Era</span>—Japanese Era for the current\n          language setup. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cqe1665702873537.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Language Setups</a><p>A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531913\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531913\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Japanese Era Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Japanese Era Use this editor to define a Japanese era of the emperors, for use with Kanji. The traditional dating system in Japan as based on the reigns of the emperors. Uniface provides language setups for modern Japanese eras in libmsg.usys.xml . Table 1. Modern Japanese Eras Date Japanese Era (Kanji) Japanese Era (Western) 1868-1912 明治 Meiji 1912-1926 大正 Taishō 1926-1989 昭和 Shōwa 1989-2019 平成 Heisei 2019 to present 令和 Reiwa You can use this dialog to define the available eras for the application. Note: You must have the Kanji font available on your machine. Fields Begin Date —date on which the selected Japanese Era is to be applied. Era —Japanese Era for the current language setup. Related Links Language Setups A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}